title: No. 3 Virginia Tech to host Kansas State on Tuesday - VT hokiesports.com
content: No. 3 Virginia Tech to host Kansas State on Tuesday  VT hokiesports.com
description: Jumping into the top three of all six leading college baseball polls this week, No. 3 Virginia Tech baseball team will begin its final chapter of the 2022 regular season on Tuesday, May 17, when the Hokies host Kansas State during non-conference play at English Field at Atlantic Union Bank Park.
